document_title: Stage 2 breast cancer: Symptoms, treatment and prognosis
subsection_name: ung-thu-vu-giai-doan-2.json_5_Prognosis of survival of stage II breast cancer patients
subsection_content: The survival rate reflects the average number of people who will survive in a given period of time. According to the American Cancer Society, the five-year survival rate for stage II breast cancer is 88-93% for women who have completed treatment.
subsection_title: ung thu vu giai doan 2.json. Prognosis of survival of stage II breast cancer patients
subsection_data:
ung thu vu giai doan 2.json. Prognosis of survival of stage II breast cancer patients
The survival rate reflects the average number of people who will survive in a given period of time. According to the American Cancer Society, the five-year survival rate for stage II breast cancer is 88-93% for women who have completed treatment.
